Prompt 2.2.5: Build Video Player Page

**Objective**: Create the video player page with comments and interactions.

**Instructions for AI Agent**:

Create the video player page in src/pages/video/[id].astro:

1. Get video ID from URL params
2. Load video data from mockData.getVideoById(id)
3. Load comments from mockData.getCommentsByVideoId(id)
4. Page structure:

<BaseLayout title={video.title}>
     <div class="video-page">
       
       <!-- Video Player Section -->
       <section class="video-player-section">
         <VideoPlayer video={video} />
         
         <!-- Video Info -->
         <div class="video-info">
           <h1 class="video-title">{video.title}</h1>
           
           <div class="video-meta">
             <div class="uploader-info">
               <img src={video.uploader.avatarUrl} class="avatar" />
               <span>{video.uploader.username}</span>
             </div>
             
             <div class="video-stats">
               <span>{video.viewCount} views</span>
               <span>{formatDate(video.uploadedAt)}</span>
             </div>
           </div>

           <!-- Action Buttons -->
           <div class="action-buttons">
             <button class="btn-like">
               👍 {video.rating.likes}
             </button>
             <button class="btn-dislike">
               👎 {video.rating.dislikes}
             </button>
             <button class="btn-favorite">
               ⭐ Add to Favorites
             </button>
           </div>

           <!-- Description -->
           <div class="description">
             <p>{video.description}</p>
           </div>

           <!-- Tags -->
           <div class="tags">
             {video.tags.map(tag => (
               <a href="#" class="tag">{tag.name}</a>
             ))}
           </div>
         </div>
       </section>

       <!-- Comments Section -->
       <section class="comments-section">
         <h2>Comments</h2>
         
         <!-- Comment Form (logged in users only - show login prompt for now) -->
         <div class="comment-form">
           <p>Please log in to comment</p>
         </div>

         <!-- Comments List -->
         <div class="comments-list">
           {comments.map(comment => (
             <CommentCard comment={comment} />
           ))}
         </div>
       </section>

       <!-- Related Videos Sidebar (Optional) -->
       <aside class="related-videos">
         <h3>Related Videos</h3>
         <!-- Show 5-10 related videos (same category or tags) -->
       </aside>

     </div>
   </BaseLayout>

   Create CommentCard component (src/components/video/CommentCard.astro):

Display comment with:

User avatar
Username
Comment text
Timestamp
Reply button (non-functional for now)


Handle nested replies (indent and recursively render)
Styling: Clean, readable, clear hierarchy


Layout:

Max width: 1400px
Two-column on desktop:

Main content (video + comments): 70%
Related videos sidebar: 30%


Single column on mobile


Styling:

Generous spacing
Clear sections
Action buttons with icons
Responsive video player that maintains aspect ratio



DELIVERABLE: Complete video player page with all sections, responsive layout, and mock interactions.
